FuncDecl.Name: AddToken
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Add a token type. Returns -1 if this operation failed.</returns> <param name="regex">The regular expression for this token type.</param> <param name="color">The color for this token type.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: AddExtraToken
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Add an extra token type. Call <links><link cref="::vl::presentation::controls::GuiTextBoxRegexColorizer::Setup()@s:vl.presentation.controls.GuiTextBoxRegexColorizer" /></links> after finishing all configuration.</summary> <returns>Returns the extra token index of this token. The token index for this token is regex-token-count + extra-token-index Returns -1 if this operation failed.</returns> <param name="color">The color for this token type.</param> </Document>
